袋里的嗡嗡声，脑袋里似乎有什么要出来，不美妙，我只是魔，我是魔，我寻求<br> <br>的是杀戮，已经猎物绝望的眼神。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 望着月亮，身后是尸体，余温尚在的尸体。奇怪的女人，我这么想。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我若为魔，当放弃一切，我若为魔，你们便不是牵挂之人，我若为魔，抱歉，GIG<br> <br>I，毛小蒙，葛琪琪，我们便无感情可言，即便是你们成为我的猎物，因为我是魔。\u0018","author":"嘻哈の大呆","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.2e2bf9d7.UI_mxvwa_6Mdp2Td2Hgfeg&fr=pb","date":"2010-07-12 09:38","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%B4%F4%CD%B7/mpic/item/8fc07dd96d0676fe39012f5e.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":3,"title":"回复：【同人】《我若为魔》（万年木写同人）","content":"别成基文....求你了...就这样..","author":"冬霜之翼","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.b2347893.3TNeoOvyjJqF50PUw2lCuA&fr=pb","date":"2010-07-12 11:39","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":4,"title":"回复：【同人】《我若为魔》（万年木写同人）","content":"<img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/jd/j_0009.gif\" width=\"40\" changedsize=\"false\">没兴趣写长篇、","author":"嘻哈の大呆","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.2e2bf9d7.UI_mxvwa_6Mdp2Td2Hgfeg&fr=pb","date":"2010-07-12 17:39","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%B4%F4%CD%B7/mpic/item/8fc07dd96d0676fe39012f5e.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":5,"title":"回复：【同人】《我若为魔》（万年木写同人）","content":"= =总觉得是梦……","author":"220.114.33.*","author_link":null,"date":"2010-07-12 18:11","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":6,"title":"回复：【同人】《我若为魔》（万年木写同人）","content":"第一帖","author":"梦醒时分我的爱","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.3172c902.KABvp2VLYHcG8iUAQnzc1w&fr=pb","date":"2010-07-12 18:52","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%C3%CE%D0%D1%CA%B1%B7%D6%CE%D2%B5%C4%B0%AE/pic/item/a36c00eac749f9ecd439c9c6.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":8,"title":"回复：【同人】《我若为魔》（万年木写同人）","content":"这…这……<br>基动了吧<br>魔这玩意不应该存在于现代吧……<br>Nero和Dante是例外而已<img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5a